u'd like to use.</p><h2 id=\"select-a-photo-and-click-embed\">Select a photo and click embed</h2><p>Open the share menu from the three dots and select <code>Embed Post</code></p><figure class=\"kg-card kg-image-card\"><img src=\"https://docs.ghost.io/content/images/2018/11/image-34.png\" class=\"kg-image\"></figure><h2 id=\"copy-the-imgur-embed-code\">Copy the Imgur embed code</h2><p>From within the embed window, click on the <code>Copy</code> button to copy the code.</p><figure class=\"kg-card kg-image-card\"><img src=\"https://docs.ghost.io/content/images/2018/11/image-36.png\" class=\"kg-image\"></figure><h2 id=\"within-the-ghost-editor-add-a-new-html-card\">Within the Ghost editor, add a new HTML card</h2><p>You can paste the form code within an HTML card on any page to embed your form</p><figure class=\"kg-card kg-image-card kg-width-wide\"><img src=\"https://docs.ghost.io/content/images/2018/09/image-3.png\" class=\"kg-image\"></figure><h2 id=\"enjoy-your-new-imgur-integration\">Enjoy your new Imgur integration</h2><p>Here's an example of a real Imgur embed in action:</p><blockquote class=\"imgur-embed-pub\" lang=\"en\" data-id=\"Vm0gcyW\" data-context=\"false\"><a href=\"//imgur.com/Vm0gcyW\">Now that the elections are finally over, I can get back to being entertained by kittens and their amusing antics.</a></blockquote><script async src=\"//s.imgur.com/min/embed.js\" charset=\"utf-8\"></script><p>Have fun!</p>","custom_template":null,"url":"https://docs.ghost.io/imgur/","uuid":"3d08130f-852d-471d-a9ce-384b5b0d8688","page":false,"codeinjection_foot":"","codeinjection_head":"","comment_id":"5ba3ecf706626b00bf606677"},"file":{"childImageSharp":{"fixed":{"base64":"data:image/png;base64,","width":30,"height":30,"src":"/static/f999857e2481e5281e1dc0eec5a292d7/2682d/integration-icon.png","srcSet":"/static/f999857e2481e5281e1dc0eec5a292d7/2682d/integration-icon.png 1x,\n/static/f999857e2481e5281e1dc0eec5a292d7/0b300/integration-icon.png 1.5x,\n/static/f999857e2481e5